HOWTO
- you need a WMFLabs account that is in the service group of 'pb': https://pb.toolforge.org/
- get the https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Manual:Pywikibot
- copy these two files from the project repository into your pybot folder
- configure your bot & update the file path to the pyapi (https://github.com/tool-labs/pb/blob/master/pyapi/wppb.py)
- create a cron job using SGE and have fun:
	jsub -once -N pers-bek-to-db-bot -mem 70m -cwd python3 pers-bek-to-db-bot.sh